Hypo Real Estate only has to pay interest on the part it takes.
The money comes from both private and public banks.
Background are losses at the daughter of Depfa.
According to a newspaper report, the state financer had refinanced himself for long-term projects for which he lent money at an extremely short notice - which is no longer possible because of the mistrust in the markets.
